On Wed, 2 Jan 2008, Bell wrote:

> I was looking at the Rotella oil today and found 5w30, straight 30wt, 5w40,
> and 15w40, but no 10w40 which is my normal winter weight oil. Is this just a
> stocking aberation on the store's part, or does it not come in 10w40?

IIRC, it does not come in 10W40.  However, the difference between 10W40
and 15W40 is very small and will not be a factor unless you have very cold
temperatures, as in the northern tier states.
